products.title: Cosplay Cleric Pin
products.description: They're finally here! #72 in the Persona Pins Lineup is the Cosplay Cleric, rendered beautifully in miniature. Size: 1" tall Looks great on a lapel! Comes with standard pin backs. Rubber pin backs available!

products.title: Hand Poured Soy Candles
products.description: Hand poured in Chico, CA, these candles are made from 100% soy wax and everything, from the jar to the wick, was made in the US! They're packed with fragrance oil for a strong punch. Each candle is 8.5 oz, and are pthalate, paraben, mica, and coloring free.

products.title: Handmade Dice Bag, Bitty Potion Bottles
products.description:
Do you need a dice bag? Well, here’s one!
The regular size dice bag measures 7 inches wide by 7 inches tall, with a sturdy pleather bottom and soft lining and can hold up to 1 lb of dice.
Large size dice bag measures 10 inches wide by 10 inches tall, also with a sturdy pleather bottom and soft lining- but this one holds up to SEVEN. POUNDS. Of dice, and is as large as my head! Big enough for most dice goblins.
